Implement functionality to:
Add/view/update/delete tasks.
Track habit streaks.
Take quick notes.
Save/load user session.
Log every action.

productivity_tracker/
├── main.py            # Main application script
├── tasks.csv          # Stores daily tasks
├── habits.json        # Stores habit tracking (e.g., water intake, reading)
├── notes.txt          # Journal or user notes
├── session.pkl        # Stores session data using Pickle
├── activity.log       # Logs app usage/events
